<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Modern Pet Form</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/start.css" />
    <style>
        .button a {
            text-decoration: none; /* Remove underline */
            color: inherit; /* Inherit text color from the parent button */
        }

            .button a:hover {
                color: inherit; /* Prevent blue color on hover */
                text-decoration: none; /* Ensure no underline */
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="steps">
                <div class="step active">
                    <span class="step-number">1</span>
                    <span>Start</span>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <span class="step-number">2</span>
                    <span>About you</span>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <span class="step-number">3</span>
                    <span>Your pet</span>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <span class="step-number">4</span>
                    <span>Confirm</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h1>Before you start...</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Please make sure you've read and agree to these points before you create a listing</p>

            <div class="info-points">
                <p>1) You won't get paid for your pet but it is free to list them with our Charity.</p>
                <p>2) We can't help with emergency rehoming. You will need to be able to keep your pet for at least 4-6 weeks minimum.</p>
                <p>3) All listings are subject to approval by our team.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="form-section">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>What type of pet do you have?</label>
                    <select>
                        <option value="">Select pet type</option>
                        <option value="dog">Dog</option>
                        <option value="cat">Cat</option>
                        <option value="bird">Bird</option>
                        <option value="other">Other</option>
                    </select>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Has your pet been neutered/spayed?</label>
                    <select>
                        <option value="">Please select</option>
                        <option value="yes">Yes</option>
                        <option value="no">No</option>
                        <option value="unknown">Not sure</option>
                    </select>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Reason for rehoming</label>
                    <select>
                        <option value="">Select reason</option>
                        <option value="moving">Moving</option>
                        <option value="allergies">Allergies</option>
                        <option value="time">Time constraints</option>
                        <option value="financial">Financial reasons</option>
                        <option value="other">Other</option> 
                    </select>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Available care period</label>
                    <select>
                        <option value="">Select duration</option>
                        <option value="1month">1 month</option>
                        <option value="2months">2 months</option>
                        <option value="3months">3 months</option>
                        <option value="flexible">Flexible</option>
                    </select>
                </div>

                <a asp-controller="Pet" asp-action="AboutYou" class="button">Next</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>